        <h2 class="section-title" id="about-heading">Who I <em>Am</em></h2>
        <div class="about-grid">
          <div class="about-text">
            <p>
              I'm a final-year B.Tech Information Technology student at <strong>Mepco Schlenk Engineering College, Sivakasi</strong>, 
              with a CGPA of <strong>8.28 / 10.00</strong> (up to Semester 6). My work lives at the intersection 
